review_blob: Very good malted beer, claer and amber color, finemedium tasting. I love it.

A flavor im not exceptionally fond of......its alright, as a light flavor with notes of sour and a fine fizz of the bubbles upon my tongue. Not proud of the aftertaste, reminded me of earthworms after a rain.
A simple taste but very satisfying.  Beautiful color and a fresh light taste.
Very refreshing and light....better out of a bottle.  Hard to believe its a radler, its so easy to drink! Joyful (:
I appreciate the fullness of this beer...its so smooth and with a suttle sweetness of banana towards the end.  Certainly one of my favorites!
